all_at_once.prompt_template:
Score this audio for each listed emotion on a 0-10 scale, where 0 means the emotion is absent and 10 means the emotion is strongly present. Return only valid JSON in exactly this format: {{"scores": {{"Emotion Name": number}}}}. Include every listed emotion exactly once, use the exact emotion names, and do not include any text outside the JSON.

Emotions:
{emotion_lines}
